(2)Higher State Educational Institution Of Ukraine "Bukovinian State Medical 
University", Chernivtsi, Ukraine.

OBJECTIVE: Introduction: The scale and socio-economic implications of the 
non-communicable diseases (NCD) epidemic are growing in Ukraine. The aim: To 
determine the mode of mortality resulted from main non-communicable diseases in 
Ukraine, calculate and estimate the number of years of potential life lost 
