working age limit 55-59 years gives the most significant loss in terms of the 
contribution in the range of 30-69 years. The structural share of the 
contribution of main NCD to the burden of premature deaths gradually increases 
with age and accumulation of chronic pathology.
CONCLUSION: Conclusions: As a result of the deaths caused by four main NCD in 
the range of 30-69 years in Ukraine in 2016, 1572.793 thousand of person-years 
or almost 56% of losses due to all causes of death at the same age were lost in 
Ukraine.

